{
  "stem": "17001.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 182.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then, by the time we get to the-- to the end of the line, they said that if you have any walking stick or if you have any soap, you should hand it over.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When my mother heard that, she said, they're not taking us to work.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If they take us to work, we have to keep ourself clean and we need the soap.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How can they take the soap away?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And why do they say the walking stick away?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was-- it was a very, very big uproar.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, it really-- it shocked the-- the-- the people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "How much time had you been on the train by then?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were there like almost four day-- no, four nights and three days.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And nobody gave soap, because the soap was rationed and whatever soap you had, it was in the bottom of the package.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they were hollering and screaming, you give the soap.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You give the soap.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You give the walking stick.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we didn't have and I said, we don't have it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then we were going and it came nighttime.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we-- we seen the sign, something written out in Polish, but we didn't-- we didn't pay attention to it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then nighttime was.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were sitting there in the-- in the train.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were sitting.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The train is not going anywhere.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then suddenly, middle of the night, the door opens with a bang and the light is coming in and the-- the striped people are coming in.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we thought that this striped-clothes men, they are crazy, that they are from the asylum or they are-- they are criminals, because who was wearing striped clothes in Europe?",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Nobody was wearing it.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
